              <p>STRAW India is not a Government funded organization. We therefore invite you to become a generous donor to ensure that our free humane education resources are made available to as many school going children across the length and breadth of India and also its remotest corners. We depend on donations to continuously expand our humane education programs, train humane educators and to create newer humane education contents, relevant for India. Our aim is to reach out to every student, during their impressionable years, year after year, so that they eventually grow up to be compassionate citizens to create a humane India.</p>
